text: arasesata te'omloka (sbami-strai) ubhaye se'i gachajopara paraa (phala) khale; lage lage te'omlokara lajjasthana te'omlokara ocarata prakasa hai ga’la, arau te'omloke jannatara gachara paterae nijake abrta karaibalai dharaile, arau adame te'omra pratipalakara adesa aman'ya karaile, phalata te'om pathabhraanta hai ga’la
